metadata.title: Quirky Powercurl V2 POP 60W Wire Organizer, Green (PPRCP-60GN)
features: VIBRANT COLOR – Quirky Powercurl Mini Pop Teal in sky blue color comes with another stylish design and bright color to choose from. The best way to fix your jumbled adapter in a stylish and convenient way.
REMOVABLE LID – Hides your excess cables in an easy way. Simply fold down the soft cover to hide your electrical mess away.
SOFT & DURABLE – Made from soft and durable silicon, bends away so you can wrap cord within its base. It then snaps over the top to hide those unsightly cables.
COMPATIBILITY - PowerCurl V2 is a cord wrap for MacBook power adapters (MacBook, 13" MacBook Pro). It makes it easy to unplug and pack up quickly.
PORTABLE & LIGHTWEIGHT – The product itself weighs only 1.6 ounces. Very lightweight and can be fit perfectly in your bag without messing what’s inside. Can be used anytime or anywhere.
description: PowerCurl is a cord wrap for MacBook power adapters (MacBook, 13" MacBook Pro). It makes it easy to unplug and pack up quickly, without having to untangle a mess the next time you set up shop.
